org.apache.xalan.processor

Class XSLTSchema

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.xalan.processor.XSLTElementDef
      • org.apache.xalan.processor.XSLTSchema

  • public class XSLTSchema
extends XSLTElementDef
    This class defines the allowed structure for an XSLT 3 stylesheet, and the mapping between Xalan classes and the markup elements in the stylesheet.
    See Also:
    XSD 1.1 Schema for XSLT Stylesheets
